Package arcade.core.sim.input

Class InputParser.Command

  • java.lang.Object
    • arcade.core.sim.input.InputParser.Command
  • Enclosing class:
    InputParser
    static class InputParser.Command
extends java.lang.Object
    Container class for arguments of a command.

    A Command object is created for each command defined from parsing command.xml.
